Centrotherm Proposes Bonus Dividend as Sales, Operating Income Increase

-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 
2011-03-23T07:06:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/centrotherm-proposes-bonus-dividend-as-sales-operating-income-increase.html
Centrotherm Photovoltaics AG (CTN) 
proposed a dividend of 50 cents plus a one-off bonus dividend of
20 cents per share, as full-year revenue and earnings before
interest and taxes increased.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
 mgavin2@bloomberg.net  